{"tid":2366403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情人就到仲未溝到新女 想搵返個ex過會唔會好賤？","createTime":"2021-01-14T12:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T13:39:55.000Z","uid":343520,"like":6,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f66d6e6267068c2a5b7ff295c45e1002064d969","tid":2366403,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"當初係我想分手嘅，佢到依家仲幾冧我<br />\n我知如果我搵返佢都好大機會復合到<br />\n但其實好老實講，我唔係想同佢復合<br />\n淨係想情人節有條女屌下，唔洗一個人過<br />\n等條賓周有得暖笠笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果真係溝唔到新女，頂住先好過冇啦<br />\n掟煲唔掟蓋，得閒做下愛，都咪話唔爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e786c523743e088a08dbc36c0bce383c039c72","tid":2366403,"uid":35348,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"好大風，頭先瞓唔着嗰陣時諗起你，發夢又諗起你，冇同你傾偈三分鐘，每秒都有諗起你，我真係未試過咁鍾意一個人，我份人好容易放棄的，但係今次一啲放棄嘅心都冇<br />\n<br />\n可能咁樣講好on9，但係，呢個係我而家嘅諗法，我好想比幸福你。"},{"pid":"cef121a8c607e52eef10850fd0a04c18bbdddaec","tid":2366403,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"吊，標題打錯左，情人「節」先啱"},{"pid":"955ae15fd998e40b50018391fe2b848fa4e0a620","tid":2366403,"uid":120729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"你淨係識搵我啲文po上連登"},{"pid":"5fcf96a16fa70172d4a5dedb07382b4033bb688f","tid":2366403,"uid":120729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"勁可悲的叫春狗。"},{"pid":"2a665baf0e8e73a745e0e50bb399aafbf989ac5d","tid":2366403,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"屌開錯名好on9，想開過個po"},{"pid":"bf36a68da17e7f06c156e996fc565afca9447582","tid":2366403,"uid":383593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy